{"word":"πορφύρα","slug":"πορφύρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πορφύρα</b></el> <el>(πορφύ˘ρα, <el>ionic</el> <el>-ρη, ἡ</el>,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πορφύρω'><el>πορφύρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>the purple-fish</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>murex</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>purple dye, purple</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>= <a href='S:πορφυρίς'><el>πορφυρίς</el></a>, <i>purple raiment</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}